	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "The Apple report has been written to `analysis/companies/apple.md`. Here's what it covers:\n\n**Structure:**\n- **Key Metrics** — Revenue ($143.8B, +16% YoY), EPS ($2.84 vs $2.67 est.), and full segment table with YoY changes\n- **Earnings Highlights** — Record quarter narrative, iPhone 17 demand drivers, Services flywheel, China +38% reversal, Wearables supply constraint explanation, Mac decline context, and management commentary on Apple Intelligence\n- **Market Reaction** — Stock +3–5% after-hours, analyst price target raises to $270–290, sentiment shift on China\n- **Forward Guidance** — Q2 FY2026 at +13–16% YoY, 48–49% gross margin, with supply constraint caveats\n- **Sector Impact** — TSMC/semiconductor implications (N3 wafer demand, CoWoS packaging), consumer electronics supply chain (Samsung OLED, Sony sensors, Foxconn assembly), and Services ecosystem effects\n- **Sources** — All primary and secondary sources listed\n\nAll figures are sourced directly from the prior research findings with specific numbers and percentages throughout." ;
