# === finding-b73574b2-a17c-4889-af4e-69a36ab28a87 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:finding-b73574b2-a17c-4889-af4e-69a36ab28a87> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-26T14:59:08.411593Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
