# === memory-c4dfdc5c-07f4-4303-9472-801da22f349a ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:memory-c4dfdc5c-07f4-4303-9472-801da22f349a> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-26T14:56:24.944985Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
