# === memory-cf784a02-21c6-4363-bfb3-787bfd491094 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:memory-cf784a02-21c6-4363-bfb3-787bfd491094> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-26T14:39:58.214921Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
